---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import DonationAsk from '../components/DonationAsk.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Aloha Critter Club | After-School Animal Clubs in Hawaii"
  description="Hawaii 501(c)(3) nonprofit building after-school clubs where kids become animal experts, practice SEL, and take action for local animal welfare."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="tagline">One Paw At A Time.</p>
    <h1>After-School Animal Clubs for Hawaii Schools</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      Aloha Critter Club partners with Hawaii Island schools to run after-school
      clubs where kids become animal experts, practice social-emotional learning,
      and take meaningful action for animals in their community.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="stats">
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-number">70</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Students served</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-number">5</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Partner schools</span>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-number">FY 2025</span>
      <span class="stat-label">Most recent year</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-snippet">
    <h2>What we do</h2>
    <p>
      Every week, kids at partner schools across Hawaii Island gather for
      after-school clubs centered on animal welfare: caring for critters,
      learning about local wildlife, practicing empathy, and taking on
      community projects for shelters and rescues.
    </p>
    <p>
      Our curriculum pairs hands-on animal education with social-emotional
      learning — building kids who can name what they feel, listen to others,
      and follow through on what they care about.
    </p>
    <p>
      <a href="/about">Meet the team →</a>
    </p>
  </section>

  <DonationAsk />
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero { padding: 2rem 0 1rem; }

  .tagline {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
  }

  .stats {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2rem 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin: 2rem 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .stat-number {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 800;
    color: var(--color-primary);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .stat-label {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .video-section {
    margin: 2rem 0 0;
  }

  .video-wrap {
    position: relative;
    aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(45, 129, 166, 0.15);
  }

  .video-wrap iframe {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    border: 0;
    display: block;
  }
</style>
